    <Label name="lblAbout" id="a46f9bc8-d57d-434b-94cd-22da155dbb44">
        <caption>The Extension Schema is available to all JADE Developers, however you may not make alterations to the source code.  Use undocumented features of the schema at your own risk - however you can request that they be considered for documentation in a future release of the schema.  Please send any queries, feature suggestions or possible faults by email to jssschema@jade.co.nz.</caption>
        <wordWrap/>
        <fontSize>8.25</fontSize>
        <foreColor>-2147483640</foreColor>
        <parent name="JSSExtensionSchemaAboutForm"/>
        <tabIndex>13</tabIndex>
